text: Just like a rainbow bright and warm after a hazy summer storm.
Flowers blooming fresh with drops of dew.
Watching you stare into the sky in the crimson sunlight. That's when I fell in love with you.
Each moment in a picture frame. I'm holding on no single shot will ever fade.
The movie of this love every part deep within my heart.
You are the spark my light in the dark. Brilliant and bold through the night.
Bright as the sun no matter what comes. We can be stars if we shine.
Don’t ever hide those feelings inside. Whenever you’re sad or you’re blue.
When you can’t cope don’t ever lose hope. The stars shine their light over you.
Every wish we’ve made has brought us here together, till forever.
Underneath the stars and moon and sun we look to the future as one.
You are the spark my light in the dark. Brilliant and bold through the night.
Bright as the sun no matter what comes. We can be stars if we shine.
